1
00:00:01,110 --> 00:00:04,410
(Episode 133)

2
00:00:06,750 --> 00:00:08,450
Ma'am, we can't afford to waste time.

3
00:00:09,380 --> 00:00:12,050
Calls from suppliers demanding payment
are bringing our operations to a halt.

4
00:00:12,050 --> 00:00:15,490
- I know.
- We need a plan, don't we?

5
00:00:17,020 --> 00:00:19,820
- Have you looked into another loan?
- It's impossible to get any more loans.

6
00:00:20,660 --> 00:00:23,290
They're already hounding us
to pay back our existing loans.

7
00:00:23,290 --> 00:00:24,660
Who's going to give us another one?

8
00:00:25,300 --> 00:00:28,270
At this point, we might have to resort
to the loan sharks in Myeong-dong.

9
00:00:32,100 --> 00:00:34,070
It's them. The loan sharks in Myeong-dong.

10
00:00:36,440 --> 00:00:37,440
Mr. Kim.

11
00:00:37,510 --> 00:00:41,350
Manager Lee was begging me.
Do you really intend to borrow from me?

12
00:00:41,950 --> 00:00:45,180
Of course. Let's meet, Mr. Kim.

13
00:00:45,480 --> 00:00:47,520
Sure, we can meet.

14
00:00:47,520 --> 00:00:49,790
But you're aware
of my interest rates, right?

15
00:00:50,020 --> 00:00:51,220
Of course. I know.

16
00:00:51,790 --> 00:00:55,760
Even a kindergartener knows
loan sharks charge insane interest.

17
00:00:56,430 --> 00:01:00,060
You can imagine how desperate I am
if I'm coming to you for money.

18
00:01:00,800 --> 00:01:03,170
Then arrange a time with Manager Lee.

19
00:01:03,870 --> 00:01:04,870
Yes.

20
00:01:06,340 --> 00:01:08,140
Are you really going to get money
from loan sharks?

21
00:01:08,340 --> 00:01:09,370
What other choice do I have?

22
00:01:09,740 --> 00:01:11,840
You were just freaking out
about us having no money.

23
00:01:12,040 --> 00:01:14,250
But the interest on those loans
is outrageous.

24
00:01:14,810 --> 00:01:15,910
If you're even a little late on a payment,

25
00:01:15,910 --> 00:01:17,780
the debt balloons
to several times the principal.

26
00:01:17,850 --> 00:01:19,880
Shut up. You think I don't know that?

27
00:01:20,420 --> 00:01:22,020
I have a plan.

28
00:01:22,790 --> 00:01:25,720
First, I'll put out this fire
and get the company back on its feet.

29
00:01:26,160 --> 00:01:28,890
Then I'll sell off
the company's prime assets and bolt.

30
00:01:29,660 --> 00:01:32,960
You go look into Martin Jang.

31
00:01:34,600 --> 00:01:35,700
Martin Jang?

32
00:01:36,300 --> 00:01:39,000
(Trustworthy Police, Safe Nation)

33
00:01:39,370 --> 00:01:41,770
I'm here to report something
about Kim Bum Seok,

34
00:01:41,770 --> 00:01:42,810
whose body was just found.

35
00:01:43,140 --> 00:01:44,540
He worked at an auto repair shop?

36
00:01:44,710 --> 00:01:45,710
Yes.

37
00:01:45,710 --> 00:01:46,910
A while ago, Chae Hwa Young...

38
00:01:47,350 --> 00:01:50,010
pushed Jang Mi's father in a parking lot
and injured him.

39
00:01:50,450 --> 00:01:54,450
Kim Bum Seok was the one who
had the dashcam footage of that incident.

40
00:01:54,650 --> 00:01:55,650
Is that right?

41
00:01:55,650 --> 00:01:58,620
He tried to blackmail Chae Hwa Young
with it for money,

42
00:01:58,920 --> 00:02:01,160
but he went missing
while being chased by Manager Lee.

43
00:02:01,430 --> 00:02:05,030
I'm sure Chae Hwa Young
and Manager Lee murdered Kim Bum Seok.

44
00:02:05,360 --> 00:02:07,770
We're also reviewing CCTV footage
as part of our investigation.

45
00:02:07,930 --> 00:02:11,340
But the body was in the water
for so long that,

46
00:02:11,340 --> 00:02:12,770
even with an autopsy,

47
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:15,410
it's unclear if we'll find any evidence.

48
00:02:15,470 --> 00:02:17,880
And there's another person, Shin Ae Ran.

49
00:02:18,110 --> 00:02:19,640
She's the girlfriend of Noh Cheol Bong,

50
00:02:19,640 --> 00:02:21,780
who died in prison taking the fall
for Chae Hwa Young.

51
00:02:22,010 --> 00:02:25,820
She's in danger, too.
Please make sure she's protected.

52
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:27,050
Shin Ae Ran, you said?

53
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:30,490
Yes, she has evidence
against Chae Hwa Young.

54
00:02:30,890 --> 00:02:32,890
And Chae Hwa Young knows it.

55
00:02:32,990 --> 00:02:36,190
Then she must be
in grave danger right now.

56
00:02:37,500 --> 00:02:41,730
- Understood.
- Detective, protect her at all costs.

57
00:02:45,170 --> 00:02:49,110
The person you're calling is unavailable.
Connecting to voicemail.

58
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:51,340
Shin Ae Ran,

59
00:02:51,980 --> 00:02:53,080
did you see the news?

60
00:02:53,550 --> 00:02:56,750
It turns out Chae Hwa Young
killed Kim Bum Seok.

61
00:02:57,950 --> 00:03:00,550
Just like your boyfriend
was wrongfully killed.

62
00:03:01,350 --> 00:03:05,460
Hiding won't solve anything.
You could be the next target.

63
00:03:05,860 --> 00:03:07,890
(General Manager Ma Seo Rin)

64
00:03:08,030 --> 00:03:12,760
Ae Ran,
please contact us so we can protect you.

65
00:03:13,330 --> 00:03:14,670
Please be safe.

66
00:03:16,870 --> 00:03:18,100
Your message has been recorded.

67
00:03:20,370 --> 00:03:21,440
Manager Lee, this won't do.

68
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:25,240
Go get Ssangkal's girlfriend. Now.

69
00:03:25,610 --> 00:03:28,950
- You mean Shin Ae Ran?
- Yes, think about it.

70
00:03:29,410 --> 00:03:32,180
The news is out
that Kim Bum Seok's body was found.

71
00:03:32,750 --> 00:03:36,750
So isn't she going to get scared
and run to Oh Jang Mi's side?

72
00:03:37,620 --> 00:03:41,190
If the evidence Ssangkal had gets
into their hands in a situation like this,

73
00:03:41,760 --> 00:03:44,830
we'll be finished before we can even
flee the country. Do you understand?

74
00:03:45,500 --> 00:03:46,500
Yes, I understand.

75
00:03:47,070 --> 00:03:48,700
I'll use all of my guys if I have to.

76
00:03:49,370 --> 00:03:51,870
I'll find that woman, Shin Ae Ran,
before Oh Jang Mi does.

77
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:54,840
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

78
00:03:57,140 --> 00:03:58,580
What if Shin Ae Ran...

79
00:03:58,940 --> 00:04:01,910
has already been taken care of
by Chae Hwa Young, just like Kim Bum Seok?

80
00:04:02,250 --> 00:04:03,310
I have a bad feeling about this.

81
00:04:03,720 --> 00:04:05,880
Chae Hwa Young must have tried
to destroy the evidence,

82
00:04:05,880 --> 00:04:07,520
which means she would have tried
to kill Shin Ae Ran.

83
00:04:07,950 --> 00:04:10,050
I really hope she managed to get away
and is hiding somewhere safe...

84
00:04:10,050 --> 00:04:12,220
after she saw you getting attacked.

85
00:04:12,620 --> 00:04:13,830
We have to hope for the best.

86
00:04:14,630 --> 00:04:18,300
Is there any way for us to find out
what happened to her?

87
00:04:18,460 --> 00:04:21,130
Lee Kang Hyuk handles everything
for Chae Hwa Young.

88
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:23,170
I'm sure he'll make a move.

89
00:04:24,070 --> 00:04:25,070
You're right.

90
00:04:25,370 --> 00:04:28,070
Or what if we secretly tail Lee Kang Hyuk?

91
00:04:28,140 --> 00:04:29,940
No, that's too dangerous.

92
00:04:31,880 --> 00:04:33,540
I have a good idea.

93
00:04:39,050 --> 00:04:40,080
(Director Kang Jun Ho)

94
00:04:40,180 --> 00:04:42,750
Director Kang, we need to talk.

95
00:04:44,160 --> 00:04:46,520
What could I possibly have
to say to you, Lawyer Kang?

96
00:04:47,790 --> 00:04:48,930
Fine, we'll talk here then.

97
00:04:50,730 --> 00:04:52,060
Did you see the news?

98
00:04:52,260 --> 00:04:55,700
About how Kim Bum Seok's body
was found in the river.

99
00:04:58,100 --> 00:04:59,100
Lawyer Kang.

100
00:05:00,470 --> 00:05:01,970
What are you implying?

101
00:05:03,040 --> 00:05:04,240
What I'm implying?

102
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:06,710
Should I spell it out right here?

103
00:05:23,460 --> 00:05:24,960
What's going on?

104
00:05:25,630 --> 00:05:26,630
A body?

105
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:32,600
Hello, Mom, I've got big news.

106
00:05:32,870 --> 00:05:34,240
Big news? What are you talking about?

107
00:05:34,770 --> 00:05:37,180
Hong Ju, pick up some meat on your way.

108
00:05:37,640 --> 00:05:40,110
We can eat it behind
Chae Hwa Young's back.

109
00:05:40,510 --> 00:05:43,180
We've been eating nothing but greens
every day,

110
00:05:43,410 --> 00:05:47,790
- and I am so sick of it.
- This is no time to think about meat.

111
00:05:48,290 --> 00:05:52,260
- I think CEO Chae killed someone.
- Again?

112
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:54,930
How many is that now?

113
00:05:55,790 --> 00:05:58,630
Does that make her a serial killer?

114
00:06:00,130 --> 00:06:01,330
That's terrifying.

115
00:06:02,200 --> 00:06:03,330
No...

116
00:06:03,500 --> 00:06:05,070
It can't be.

117
00:06:05,440 --> 00:06:06,770
I hope that's not right.

118
00:06:06,770 --> 00:06:08,940
That's going too far.

119
00:06:09,310 --> 00:06:12,040
Hong Ju, no matter how much
you may hate Chae Hwa Young,

120
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:15,550
- you shouldn't accuse people like that.
- I'm not accusing her.

121
00:06:17,420 --> 00:06:19,780
Just now, Baek Ho took Jun Ho outside...

122
00:06:19,780 --> 00:06:22,120
while talking about
the body from the news.

123
00:06:22,450 --> 00:06:25,460
And Jun Ho couldn't say a peep
and just went with him.

124
00:06:26,390 --> 00:06:29,290
Something's definitely up.

125
00:06:29,290 --> 00:06:31,100
When CEO Chae went to prison,

126
00:06:31,230 --> 00:06:33,130
the way she got out was suspicious,
wasn't it?

127
00:06:33,630 --> 00:06:34,630
Oh my gosh.

128
00:06:35,230 --> 00:06:40,200
So are you saying Chae Hwa Young
was really the killer in that murder case?

129
00:06:43,980 --> 00:06:45,710
What are you talking about?

130
00:06:45,980 --> 00:06:49,110
Hwa Young's the killer in a murder case?

131
00:06:49,110 --> 00:06:50,150
You scared me.

132
00:06:51,280 --> 00:06:52,280
Hong Ju, I'll call you back.

133
00:06:52,850 --> 00:06:54,820
I asked what you were talking about.

134
00:06:54,990 --> 00:06:58,360
Why were you eavesdropping
on a private conversation?

135
00:06:58,460 --> 00:07:01,760
If you're a professor, act like one.
Have some class.

136
00:07:01,990 --> 00:07:05,800
I bet that professor title is a total lie.

137
00:07:05,860 --> 00:07:09,330
- What? A lie?
- Yes, a lie.

138
00:07:09,970 --> 00:07:11,300
Unbelievable.

139
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:12,800
Move.

140
00:07:13,570 --> 00:07:15,840
This is ridiculous.

141
00:07:17,070 --> 00:07:18,080
Professor Kang.

142
00:07:18,110 --> 00:07:23,080
Finish trimming those vegetables
I was working on.

143
00:07:23,210 --> 00:07:26,650
What? You want me to trim vegetables?

144
00:07:26,880 --> 00:07:31,290
How can you be so shameless? You expect
a free meal without lifting a finger?

145
00:07:31,590 --> 00:07:35,690
You do know how shameless that is, right,
Professor Kang?

146
00:07:40,670 --> 00:07:44,600
She's even better at getting on my nerves
than Han Young Ja.

147
00:07:46,100 --> 00:07:48,410
But Hwa Young...

148
00:07:49,270 --> 00:07:50,810
is a murderer?

149
00:07:51,610 --> 00:07:54,480
No, it can't be. That's ridiculous.

150
00:07:55,910 --> 00:07:57,150
What are you trying to say?

151
00:07:58,450 --> 00:08:00,250
Are you saying that CEO Chae
committed murder?

152
00:08:00,550 --> 00:08:03,790
He's the one who blackmailed CEO Chae
with the dashcam footage of her crime.

153
00:08:04,990 --> 00:08:08,260
He was being chased by Lee Kang Hyuk,
and then his body was found.

154
00:08:08,430 --> 00:08:10,760
That dashcam footage was already
on the news,

155
00:08:11,060 --> 00:08:13,660
and CEO Chae was cleared of all charges
a long time ago.

156
00:08:13,730 --> 00:08:15,470
He was killed before it was on the news.

157
00:08:16,230 --> 00:08:17,640
CEO Chae was trying to stop...

158
00:08:18,100 --> 00:08:20,840
I mean, she was trying to shut him up.

159
00:08:22,040 --> 00:08:24,010
Though the footage ended up
on the news anyway.

160
00:08:25,010 --> 00:08:26,680
But that doesn't mean CEO Chae
would commit murder.

161
00:08:27,180 --> 00:08:28,650
You're a lawyer,

162
00:08:28,650 --> 00:08:30,080
and you're making accusations
without any evidence?

163
00:08:30,080 --> 00:08:31,680
I may not have evidence,
but I'm a witness.

164
00:08:32,450 --> 00:08:34,090
The day I went to see Kim Bum Seok,

165
00:08:34,290 --> 00:08:36,490
I saw him being chased
by Lee Kang Hyuk's men.

166
00:08:37,190 --> 00:08:39,760
After that, Kim Bum Seok disappeared.

167
00:08:40,990 --> 00:08:42,890
Isn't that enough to be suspicious?

168
00:08:44,330 --> 00:08:45,430
And more importantly,

169
00:08:46,130 --> 00:08:48,000
another person might die.

170
00:08:49,230 --> 00:08:50,370
Her name is Shin Ae Ran.

171
00:08:51,370 --> 00:08:53,840
She's the girlfriend of Ssangkal
who went to prison for CEO Chae.

172
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:55,370
And now, she's missing.

173
00:08:56,210 --> 00:08:58,440
If you don't want
any more innocent victims to die,

174
00:08:59,040 --> 00:09:00,040
stop Lee Kang Hyuk.

175
00:09:00,910 --> 00:09:01,910
As your younger brother,

176
00:09:02,580 --> 00:09:03,780
I'm begging you.

177
00:09:09,450 --> 00:09:10,450
What happened?

178
00:09:11,160 --> 00:09:13,060
Have you still not found any trace
of Shin Ae Ran?

179
00:09:13,420 --> 00:09:16,660
No, but I have my men on it.
We should know something soon.

180
00:09:18,060 --> 00:09:19,460
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

181
00:09:20,060 --> 00:09:21,070
Jun Ho.

182
00:09:22,770 --> 00:09:24,000
Let me ask you one thing, Manager Lee.

183
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:27,140
Did you kill the man named Kim Bum Seok?

184
00:09:27,710 --> 00:09:29,340
What are you talking about, Jun Ho?

185
00:09:29,770 --> 00:09:32,880
Why would I kill him?
I don't even know who Kim Bum Seok is.

186
00:09:34,310 --> 00:09:35,350
CEO Chae Hwa Young,

187
00:09:36,050 --> 00:09:37,080
let me ask you one thing.

188
00:09:37,820 --> 00:09:39,620
Did you kill the man named Kim Bum Seok?

189
00:09:39,950 --> 00:09:42,350
Jun Ho, what have you heard
that's making you act this way?

190
00:09:42,690 --> 00:09:44,960
You killed Kim Bum Seok
because he blackmailed you,

191
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:48,830
and now is it Shin Ae Ran's turn to die
because she has evidence?

192
00:09:49,090 --> 00:09:51,800
Did Oh Jang Mi and Kang Baek Ho
tell you that nonsense?

193
00:09:52,430 --> 00:09:54,030
You don't need to listen to them.

194
00:09:54,300 --> 00:09:56,730
What does a human life even mean to you?

195
00:09:57,800 --> 00:09:59,140
What if I died for you?

196
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:03,210
Even if I died, you wouldn't even
bat an eye, would you?

197
00:10:04,540 --> 00:10:05,540
Right?

198
00:10:08,550 --> 00:10:10,920
Jun Ho, no. Wait.

199
00:10:10,980 --> 00:10:12,980
Jun Ho, you're all I have.

200
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:14,190
Jun Ho.

201
00:10:14,290 --> 00:10:16,290
(Computer Investigation Room)

202
00:10:16,890 --> 00:10:19,120
Shin Ae Ran, did you see the news?

203
00:10:19,660 --> 00:10:22,860
It turns out Chae Hwa Young
killed Kim Bum Seok.

204
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:25,960
Just like your boyfriend
was wrongfully killed.

205
00:10:26,900 --> 00:10:30,970
Hiding won't solve anything.
You could be the next target.

206
00:10:36,740 --> 00:10:39,010
How can I help you?

207
00:10:39,780 --> 00:10:40,850
I'm here to file a report.

208
00:10:41,350 --> 00:10:43,880
Please reopen Noh Cheol Bong's case.

209
00:10:44,480 --> 00:10:46,720
- I have evidence.
- Noh Cheol Bong...

210
00:10:47,720 --> 00:10:48,850
Shin Ae Ran...

211
00:10:49,050 --> 00:10:50,090
You're Shin Ae Ran, right?

212
00:10:50,920 --> 00:10:51,920
Do you know me?

213
00:10:52,690 --> 00:10:53,690
Here.

214
00:10:54,160 --> 00:10:56,890
I've brought evidence that Chae Hwa Young
murdered Mr. Oh Bok Gil.

215
00:10:58,030 --> 00:11:00,500
Please, you have to prove
my Cheol Bong's innocence.

216
00:11:00,930 --> 00:11:01,930
Please.

217
00:11:07,140 --> 00:11:08,140
This is...

218
00:11:09,210 --> 00:11:10,240
a wrench?

219
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:18,250
So, you're saying you intentionally leaked
information about Shin Ae Ran...

220
00:11:18,250 --> 00:11:19,520
to Jun Ho?

221
00:11:20,020 --> 00:11:24,060
Yes, it was obvious Kang Jun Ho would try
to confirm the facts with Lee Kang Hyuk.

222
00:11:24,390 --> 00:11:27,830
Then Lee Kang Hyuk will make a move
after hearing it from Jun Ho.

223
00:11:28,130 --> 00:11:30,560
If he finds out we're looking
for Shin Ae Ran,

224
00:11:30,560 --> 00:11:31,800
he'll try to find her first.

225
00:11:31,960 --> 00:11:33,460
When Lee Kang Hyuk makes his move,

226
00:11:33,830 --> 00:11:37,130
we can follow him
using the tracking app we installed.

227
00:11:38,100 --> 00:11:39,970
And we'll be able to save Shin Ae Ran.

228
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:41,470
Exactly, Mom.

229
00:11:41,810 --> 00:11:43,870
Now all we have to do is wait
for Lee Kang Hyuk to make a move.

230
00:11:44,480 --> 00:11:45,580
Right.

231
00:11:47,180 --> 00:11:50,410
But I'm worried about
how Jun Ho must be feeling.

232
00:11:51,980 --> 00:11:54,890
His biological parents are murdering
people left and right. Good grief.

233
00:11:55,590 --> 00:11:58,960
Why was he born to parents like that...

234
00:11:59,320 --> 00:12:00,930
He couldn't help that.

235
00:12:01,430 --> 00:12:03,390
He couldn't choose his parents.

236
00:12:03,690 --> 00:12:07,160
He can still be a good, decent person.

237
00:12:08,630 --> 00:12:10,130
That's true.

238
00:12:10,130 --> 00:12:11,200
But still...

239
00:12:11,970 --> 00:12:13,400
I feel bad for Jun Ho.

240
00:12:13,470 --> 00:12:16,110
He needs to get a grip
so he doesn't end up like his parents.

241
00:12:16,440 --> 00:12:17,710
That's up to him.

242
00:12:22,150 --> 00:12:23,280
Yes, Detective Kim.

243
00:12:25,280 --> 00:12:26,280
What?

244
00:12:26,920 --> 00:12:28,850
Did you say Shin Ae Ran left the wrench?

245
00:12:29,820 --> 00:12:31,090
And the recording file Ssangkal had?

246
00:12:31,720 --> 00:12:34,990
That's the smoking gun that proves
Chae Hwa Young murdered Oh Bok Gil.

247
00:12:36,160 --> 00:12:38,730
(Trustworthy Police, Safe Nation)

248
00:12:39,300 --> 00:12:41,500
Oh Jang Mi just left the house.

249
00:12:41,670 --> 00:12:42,670
Good.

250
00:12:42,670 --> 00:12:44,970
We can't mess this up, so stay sharp.

251
00:12:45,470 --> 00:12:46,600
Take care of Oh Jang Mi.

252
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:48,570
Make it look like an accident.
Keep it clean.

253
00:12:50,940 --> 00:12:55,180
This is the evidence
that they hit Seo Rin and me with a truck.

254
00:12:56,280 --> 00:12:59,950
That day, Seo Rin was hurt instead of me,
and she was bedridden for a long time.

255
00:13:01,250 --> 00:13:02,290
Jang Mi.

256
00:13:04,490 --> 00:13:07,730
With this, we can prove Lee Kang Hyuk
and Chae Hwa Young are guilty.

257
00:13:08,760 --> 00:13:11,260
There's more evidence.
Let's listen to the rest.

258
00:13:16,270 --> 00:13:18,800
You're the only one
with a connection to Oh Bok Gil.

259
00:13:19,540 --> 00:13:21,110
You're taking the fall for CEO Chae.

260
00:13:21,440 --> 00:13:24,340
What if the arrangements
you've made fall through?

261
00:13:26,040 --> 00:13:28,780
It's a recording of Kang Hyuk trying
to get Chae Hwa Young out of jail.

262
00:13:29,280 --> 00:13:31,920
He's persuading Ssangkal
to take the fall for her.

263
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:33,880
Yes, that seems to be the case.

264
00:13:34,220 --> 00:13:37,290
So this is how Chae Hwa Young
has gotten away with it all this time.

265
00:13:38,390 --> 00:13:40,860
Anyway, now that we have the wrench,

266
00:13:41,230 --> 00:13:43,590
Chae Hwa Young won't be able
to get away this time.

267
00:13:44,700 --> 00:13:46,500
Detective, please submit the evidence...

268
00:13:46,930 --> 00:13:49,330
to the Prosecutor's Office
and get a warrant.

269
00:13:49,670 --> 00:13:51,800
Then we can arrest
Chae Hwa Young right away.

270
00:13:52,270 --> 00:13:54,370
But we have to find Shin Ae Ran.

271
00:13:54,840 --> 00:13:58,710
Lee Kang Hyuk will try to kill her
to stop her from testifying.

272
00:14:02,150 --> 00:14:03,250
Yes, Detective Lee.

273
00:14:05,220 --> 00:14:06,280
What did you say?

274
00:14:07,180 --> 00:14:09,020
Shin Ae Ran submitted the evidence?

275
00:14:10,650 --> 00:14:12,220
Then we're in big trouble, aren't we?

276
00:14:12,720 --> 00:14:14,530
Whatever you do,
make that evidence disappear.

277
00:14:15,530 --> 00:14:16,730
Yes. You have to.

278
00:14:17,460 --> 00:14:18,530
What on earth are you talking about?

279
00:14:19,300 --> 00:14:21,400
Why does Shin Ae Ran have the wrench?

280
00:14:21,870 --> 00:14:23,000
Calm down, Hwa Young.

281
00:14:23,470 --> 00:14:25,870
Detective Lee said
he'd swipe the evidence,

282
00:14:26,170 --> 00:14:28,070
- it'll be fine.
- And you expect me to calm down?

283
00:14:28,310 --> 00:14:29,810
What if Detective Lee can't get it?

284
00:14:30,170 --> 00:14:32,840
Then I'll be arrested for murder
with no escape.

285
00:14:33,180 --> 00:14:34,280
Besides, you said...

286
00:14:34,280 --> 00:14:37,210
there's a recording of you
pressuring Ssangkal to confess, right?

287
00:14:38,650 --> 00:14:39,720
I'm sorry.

288
00:14:40,250 --> 00:14:41,650
That bastard Ssangkal recorded everything,

289
00:14:42,890 --> 00:14:45,220
from how I ordered him
to kill Oh Jang Mi...

290
00:14:45,590 --> 00:14:47,730
and told him to take the fall for you,
Hwa Young.

291
00:14:48,630 --> 00:14:50,160
He recorded it all.

292
00:14:50,290 --> 00:14:53,300
How could you let him record you?
Are you insane?

293
00:14:53,360 --> 00:14:55,500
How can you have an appetite
after leaving a loose end like that?

294
00:14:55,730 --> 00:14:57,600
Why does everything you touch
turn into a disaster?

295
00:14:58,240 --> 00:15:00,370
I'll find Shin Ae Ran right now
and shut her up...

296
00:15:00,370 --> 00:15:01,710
so she can't testify or anything.

297
00:15:01,770 --> 00:15:03,240
Find her now.

298
00:15:03,840 --> 00:15:04,840
I will.

299
00:15:08,780 --> 00:15:10,080
Unbelievable.

300
00:15:11,080 --> 00:15:13,080
I don't get a single day of peace.

301
00:15:24,030 --> 00:15:25,530
Yes, this is Oh Jang Mi.

302
00:15:25,960 --> 00:15:26,960
Hello.

303
00:15:27,560 --> 00:15:28,870
This is Shin Ae Ran.

304
00:15:29,600 --> 00:15:30,600
Ae Ran.

305
00:15:35,040 --> 00:15:36,410
You must be tired.

306
00:15:36,410 --> 00:15:38,780
- We're home.
- You're here.

307
00:15:39,180 --> 00:15:43,150
The shop is so busy, so you two
don't even have a moment to breathe.

308
00:15:44,050 --> 00:15:46,550
- Is Bo Ra asleep?
- I just put her to bed.

309
00:15:49,320 --> 00:15:51,460
Look! Lee Kang Hyuk is making his move.

310
00:15:52,590 --> 00:15:54,430
(Toegyero 4-ga)

311
00:15:59,930 --> 00:16:03,500
Baek Ho. I'm not sure
when Manager Lee started to move,

312
00:16:03,630 --> 00:16:07,200
- but he's on the move now.
- What? Manager Lee is on the move?

313
00:16:07,370 --> 00:16:09,610
Ae Ran, we've been waiting for you.

314
00:16:10,170 --> 00:16:11,980
We'll come to you. Where are you?

315
00:16:11,980 --> 00:16:14,080
Tae Pyung, where's Manager Lee heading?

316
00:16:14,450 --> 00:16:15,680
- Banghwa-dong?
- Banghwa-dong?

317
00:16:17,680 --> 00:16:20,480
Was it a call saying
Manager Lee is heading to Banghwa-dong?

318
00:16:20,880 --> 00:16:21,890
Yes.

319
00:16:23,290 --> 00:16:26,020
Shin Ae Ran, are you at your home
in Banghwa-dong right now?

320
00:16:26,360 --> 00:16:27,730
Get out of there right now.

321
00:16:28,130 --> 00:16:29,930
It looks like your hideout
has been discovered.

322
00:16:30,160 --> 00:16:31,730
Manager Lee is heading your way.

323
00:16:31,860 --> 00:16:34,530
Get rid of your phone, now.
There's no time.

324
00:16:34,770 --> 00:16:37,840
Get out of there
and call me from a pay phone.

325
00:16:37,940 --> 00:16:39,100
I'll head that way too.

326
00:17:11,540 --> 00:17:12,700
Darn it.

327
00:17:15,540 --> 00:17:16,870
She just got away.

328
00:17:17,270 --> 00:17:20,310
Comb the area.
Don't let a single rat escape.

329
00:17:20,480 --> 00:17:21,580
- Yes, sir.
- Yes, sir.

330
00:17:24,250 --> 00:17:26,380
(Pay Phone)

331
00:17:26,450 --> 00:17:29,990
Hello? Jang Mi, this is Shin Ae Ran.

332
00:17:30,220 --> 00:17:33,320
Ae Ran, are you hurt? Where are you now?

333
00:17:34,190 --> 00:17:35,990
I'm at a pay phone
near Banghwa Intersection.

334
00:17:36,430 --> 00:17:37,760
Please, hurry.

335
00:17:38,730 --> 00:17:39,730
Okay.

336
00:17:47,700 --> 00:17:48,740
Found you.

337
00:17:51,180 --> 00:17:53,180
- Drag her out.
- No. Stay away.

338
00:17:53,380 --> 00:17:54,380
Stay away.

339
00:17:55,050 --> 00:17:56,510
Please, stay away.

340
00:17:56,810 --> 00:17:58,550
(Pay Phone)

341
00:18:11,430 --> 00:18:12,430
Get your hands off her!

342
00:18:12,430 --> 00:18:15,170
Lee Kang Hyuk.
Stop being Chae Hwa Young's lackey.

343
00:18:15,230 --> 00:18:16,230
Kang Baek Ho.

344
00:18:16,230 --> 00:18:17,230
Oh Jang Mi.

345
00:18:17,770 --> 00:18:20,740
How did you know I was here?
You've got a lot of nerve.

346
00:18:22,010 --> 00:18:23,140
Get them first.

347
00:18:23,510 --> 00:18:26,310
Grab them and break their legs
so they can never walk again.

348
00:18:48,300 --> 00:18:49,630
Bring it on.

349
00:19:00,310 --> 00:19:01,310
Darn it.

350
00:19:01,980 --> 00:19:03,150
- Let's go.
- Yes, sir.

351
00:19:03,150 --> 00:19:04,410
Darn it.

352
00:19:06,420 --> 00:19:08,650
- Are you okay?
- Yes.

353
00:19:24,000 --> 00:19:25,070
Detective.

354
00:19:25,640 --> 00:19:26,770
What about the evidence?

355
00:19:27,700 --> 00:19:29,770
The wrench that Shin Ae Ran submitted.

356
00:19:30,370 --> 00:19:31,410
Hand it over now.

357
00:19:33,080 --> 00:19:34,950
Calm down, ma'am.

358
00:19:35,580 --> 00:19:38,280
Just give me the money,
and I'll take care of everything.

359
00:19:38,620 --> 00:19:40,050
Surely you know what I'm capable of.

360
00:19:42,990 --> 00:19:46,220
I swiped it before it went
to the evidence room.

361
00:19:46,420 --> 00:19:50,330
I'll give you whatever money you want,
just give me the wrench now.

362
00:19:50,430 --> 00:19:54,060
With this evidence,
you're definitely going to prison.

363
00:19:54,460 --> 00:19:57,130
Cut the nonsense and just give it to me.

364
00:19:58,370 --> 00:19:59,600
Money first.

365
00:19:59,940 --> 00:20:02,770
If you take it and run away with it,
I’ll be left with nothing.

366
00:20:03,170 --> 00:20:06,540
Rumor has it Dream Hotel
is in some serious financial trouble,

367
00:20:06,740 --> 00:20:08,780
I wonder if you even have the money
to give me.

368
00:20:09,880 --> 00:20:13,320
This is a very valuable item, you know.

369
00:20:15,250 --> 00:20:16,850
Fine, I get it.

370
00:20:23,790 --> 00:20:26,060
Mr. Kim, I'm in a bind right now.

371
00:20:27,230 --> 00:20:29,200
- Just give me 1 million dollars...
- No, 2 million dollars.

372
00:20:35,040 --> 00:20:36,770
Just give me a quick loan
for two million dollars.

373
00:20:37,370 --> 00:20:39,440
With 50 percent interest paid upfront,
of course.

374
00:20:40,240 --> 00:20:41,780
And make it three million dollars.

375
00:20:42,050 --> 00:20:43,250
Wait, five million dollars.

376
00:20:45,820 --> 00:20:46,850
He says to wait.

377
00:20:48,320 --> 00:20:49,790
Anyway, thank you, Mr. Kim.

378
00:20:50,220 --> 00:20:52,260
Let's meet tomorrow
to discuss the details.

379
00:20:56,430 --> 00:20:58,200
Was two million dollars too low of an ask?

380
00:20:58,330 --> 00:21:00,600
I'll send the two million dollars,
so just give me the wrench.

381
00:21:03,230 --> 00:21:05,170
Okay, let's make an exchange.

382
00:21:18,420 --> 00:21:19,580
I sent it.

383
00:21:19,820 --> 00:21:21,890
Make sure you handle things properly
for me.

384
00:21:25,160 --> 00:21:27,920
Thanks to you,
I think I'll be able to buy a house.

385
00:21:28,660 --> 00:21:31,230
I could never afford one
on a police salary.

386
00:21:37,800 --> 00:21:40,140
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

387
00:21:53,720 --> 00:21:55,690
I can't believe
this is worth five million dollars.

388
00:22:03,130 --> 00:22:04,160
Yes, Manager Lee.

389
00:22:04,490 --> 00:22:05,560
Ma'am.

390
00:22:05,560 --> 00:22:07,760
Kang Baek Ho and Oh Jang Mi
took Shin Ae Ran.

391
00:22:07,760 --> 00:22:08,770
What should I do?

392
00:22:09,200 --> 00:22:11,800
- Should I follow them to the end?
- No, just let them go.

393
00:22:12,870 --> 00:22:16,110
Detective Lee successfully
swiped the evidence for us.

394
00:22:16,410 --> 00:22:17,810
Yes, understood.

395
00:22:24,250 --> 00:22:25,250
What is this?

396
00:22:42,830 --> 00:22:45,770
What brought you here so late at night?

397
00:22:50,910 --> 00:22:52,910
You fooled me completely.

398
00:22:53,780 --> 00:22:56,450
You were the one who went through my car
and stole the receipt...

399
00:22:57,710 --> 00:22:59,720
and planted the tracker on my phone.

400
00:23:02,090 --> 00:23:03,820
It was all you, Young Ja, wasn't it?

401
00:23:05,120 --> 00:23:07,160
Because you're Jun Ho's biological father.

402
00:23:09,390 --> 00:23:10,530
And on the other hand,

403
00:23:11,460 --> 00:23:13,660
your life was just so pitiful,

404
00:23:14,830 --> 00:23:16,170
so I wanted to give you a chance.

405
00:23:17,100 --> 00:23:18,240
From the very beginning,

406
00:23:20,400 --> 00:23:23,070
did you approach me
with such a shallow motive?

407
00:23:23,970 --> 00:23:24,980
That's right.

408
00:23:25,580 --> 00:23:27,680
Please, just snap out of it.

409
00:23:28,750 --> 00:23:29,750
What did you say?

410
00:23:30,410 --> 00:23:32,480
Stop letting Chae Hwa Young use you.

411
00:23:33,280 --> 00:23:35,290
Leave Chae Hwa Young, please.

412
00:23:35,850 --> 00:23:37,050
Take Jun Ho...

413
00:23:37,820 --> 00:23:40,360
and get out of that toxic house.

414
00:23:40,690 --> 00:23:44,260
The only person
who can get Jun Ho out of there...

415
00:23:44,730 --> 00:23:46,800
is you, his father.

416
00:23:47,430 --> 00:23:49,370
If you love Jun Ho,

417
00:23:49,770 --> 00:23:51,270
then please,

418
00:23:51,600 --> 00:23:55,010
stop your evil ways and be there for him.

419
00:23:55,240 --> 00:23:57,940
- Stop it.
- If you would just do that,

420
00:23:58,780 --> 00:24:02,650
I'll help you no matter what,
so you can get a reduced sentence.

421
00:24:02,710 --> 00:24:05,750
As a lawyer,
I'll do my best for you. Okay?

422
00:24:08,920 --> 00:24:11,420
Surrender is not an option for me.

423
00:24:13,260 --> 00:24:14,560
Young Ja.

424
00:24:15,290 --> 00:24:17,990
I don't know what you think you know
about me to talk so recklessly,

425
00:24:19,330 --> 00:24:20,330
but do you know...

426
00:24:22,300 --> 00:24:25,370
how hard I worked
serving CEO Chae to get to this position?

427
00:24:27,470 --> 00:24:29,170
Are you going to just look back
at the road you've traveled...

428
00:24:29,810 --> 00:24:32,440
and throw the rest of your future
in the trash?

429
00:24:32,810 --> 00:24:34,410
Stop looking back.

430
00:24:35,150 --> 00:24:39,350
Just look ahead to the life you can have
with Jun Ho, please.

431
00:24:39,450 --> 00:24:42,050
From now on, don't act like
you know anything about my son.

432
00:24:42,590 --> 00:24:44,220
I'll pretend I don't know you,

433
00:24:45,260 --> 00:24:47,220
so don't you ever interfere again.

434
00:24:57,570 --> 00:24:59,640
- They're here.
- Mother.

435
00:24:59,870 --> 00:25:00,970
You all did well.

436
00:25:05,810 --> 00:25:07,640
Is Shin Ae Ran safe?

437
00:25:07,780 --> 00:25:11,010
Yes. Detective Kim is keeping her safe.

438
00:25:11,150 --> 00:25:12,880
Did Dad leave?

439
00:25:13,720 --> 00:25:14,720
No.

440
00:25:16,290 --> 00:25:19,460
You were all working so hard.
How could I just stay in my hotel room?

441
00:25:21,790 --> 00:25:22,790
Shall we have a drink?

442
00:25:30,930 --> 00:25:33,840
- You must've missed Korean soju, right?
- Yes.

443
00:25:37,910 --> 00:25:40,110
I really missed this taste.

444
00:25:41,880 --> 00:25:44,280
I hear you're Choi Ha Joon.

445
00:25:45,550 --> 00:25:47,980
- You knew?
- My father told me.

446
00:25:48,890 --> 00:25:52,490
I knew your grandfather,
Chairman Choi Myung Chul, quite well.

447
00:25:53,760 --> 00:25:54,790
You did?

448
00:25:59,730 --> 00:26:03,570
I was so surprised to find out
about your connection to my Jang Mi.

449
00:26:03,800 --> 00:26:07,940
I only knew that my grandfather
and the Chairman were friends.

450
00:26:08,070 --> 00:26:09,470
I don't know anything beyond that.

451
00:26:09,470 --> 00:26:12,040
After your parents died in a car accident,

452
00:26:12,640 --> 00:26:14,010
Chairman Choi Myung Chul...

453
00:26:15,050 --> 00:26:17,250
doted on you.

454
00:26:17,480 --> 00:26:20,720
Do you happen to know
how my grandfather died?

455
00:26:21,220 --> 00:26:25,390
And do you know anything
about why I ended up in an orphanage?

456
00:26:25,860 --> 00:26:27,160
The fire back then...

457
00:26:28,020 --> 00:26:30,030
was an accident caused by your nanny.

458
00:26:31,460 --> 00:26:35,630
Tragically, your grandfather died
right after saving you.

459
00:26:36,170 --> 00:26:38,340
Racked with guilt,

460
00:26:38,470 --> 00:26:41,840
the nanny abandoned you at an orphanage
and ran away.

461
00:26:43,410 --> 00:26:44,470
So that's what happened...

462
00:26:44,510 --> 00:26:48,450
A few years later, the nanny was caught,

463
00:26:48,950 --> 00:26:51,550
and we found out she had abandoned you
at the orphanage.

464
00:26:51,780 --> 00:26:53,480
But by then,
we'd received false information...

465
00:26:53,480 --> 00:26:56,090
that you'd been adopted overseas.

466
00:26:56,420 --> 00:26:59,220
That's why we couldn't find you.

467
00:27:00,990 --> 00:27:04,630
- I see.
- After failing to find you, my father...

468
00:27:05,660 --> 00:27:07,560
honored Chairman Choi's last wishes.

469
00:27:08,200 --> 00:27:09,370
Chairman Choi...

470
00:27:10,300 --> 00:27:11,470
had terminal cancer.

471
00:27:12,200 --> 00:27:13,340
My grandfather...

472
00:27:14,200 --> 00:27:15,210
had terminal cancer?

473
00:27:15,270 --> 00:27:17,240
That's why he transferred the land
for the Dream Hotel...

474
00:27:17,240 --> 00:27:19,210
to my father long ago...

475
00:27:20,110 --> 00:27:23,310
and entrusted all his stocks and assets
in Choi Ha Joon's name.

476
00:27:23,880 --> 00:27:25,920
He told my father to hand them
over to you when you came of age.

477
00:27:26,580 --> 00:27:29,950
That's why my father
never filed your death certificate...

478
00:27:30,520 --> 00:27:31,990
and kept waiting for you.

479
00:27:34,720 --> 00:27:36,290
The true owner of Dream...

480
00:27:37,760 --> 00:27:38,830
is you.

481
00:28:05,120 --> 00:28:06,760
(The First Man)

482
00:28:06,860 --> 00:28:08,560
There's no evidence left now.

483
00:28:08,830 --> 00:28:11,730
No, I have the real wrench.

484
00:28:12,360 --> 00:28:15,500
So you've been taking her money
and backing Chae Hwa Young all this time.

485
00:28:15,700 --> 00:28:17,870
Any information from the investigation
that goes to Chae Hwa Young,

486
00:28:17,930 --> 00:28:19,600
you report to us first.

487
00:28:19,740 --> 00:28:22,070
Are you going to sell Dream Hotel
to Martin Jang?

488
00:28:22,240 --> 00:28:25,980
I'll leave an empty shell
and take all the good stuff for myself.

489
00:28:26,110 --> 00:28:28,980
Just as Jang Mi said,
I'll turn you into a beggar,

490
00:28:29,050 --> 00:28:31,110
and utterly destroy you.

491
00:28:32,250 --> 00:28:34,250
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
